EDO Corp said McDonnell Aircraf Co hasinvoked its 1987 production option calling for ejection releaseunits for the F-15E aircraft.    The company said the contract is not to exceed 10.1 mlndlrs and will be handled by its government systems division inCollege Point, N.Y.    The company said the contract is a follow up to the fullscale development and 1986 contracts previously awarded to EDO. Reuter&#3;